What YouTube Creators Think of the Site’s Major New Change 
Time Saturday 24th October, 2015 
The free ad-supported version of YouTube will continue on mostly unabated as it has for the past decade. But the new initiative marks the beginning of a new chapter for the world’s largest video site. While YouTube has experimented with subscriptions for...
